          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主 （同江儿水） 痛王家骨肉身难保。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "崇祯帝 （五供养） 我也曾食旰衣宵，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十七载王事辛劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "停乐不逍遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁料上天不佑保。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回首苍穹泪血空抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀不好了吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王承恩、费贞娥同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀陛下不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天灾到，贼兵百万布城壕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那杜勋呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他奸谋狡，启关迎寇长驱捣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "娘娘、太子、公主",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠮾！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎贲龙骧呈散逃！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休逆料，潜身逃遁须趁早。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（五供养） 仓忙觅道，仓忙觅道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苍天哪，天！朝廷上下，分崩离析。勤王无师，立锥无地。朕惟有一死——"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠮾……"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，以谢天下。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人 （同哭） 喂呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可惜你生之不辰，罹遭国难。你可外穿民服，内藏玉牒，逃奔他乡，虽不指望"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你中兴，尚可继续宗祧。你速速改装，逃命去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "太子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀父王吓！儿臣不肖，不能为国抒忠，以致国家沦亡，今日岂敢偷生逃遁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这生死——愿同一处的哟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！胡说，你欲同死，何益于事？若不逃往他处，必然绝灭宗祧，岂非天地间"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "之大罪人吗？快去、快去、快去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（费贞娥陪太子同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀爱卿哪！当此国破家亡之际，可恨满朝文武各顾家身。今秉忠仗义，惟汝"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一人，你今保护太子逃命去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陛下。奴婢受陛下雨露深恩，粉身难报。今当保太子出宫潜藏僻静村庄，况太"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子生处无人厮认，奴婢当竭力保护，请万岁爷放心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿乃大忠臣也。你……改装去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王承恩下，太子便装上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "太子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父王，父王！啊呀！吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿，我儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太子 （同千秋岁） 泪如潮，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急嚷嚷逃奔荒郊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只索向海角天涯飘渺。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离群雁生难料。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "覆巢卵谁能保？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "逃脱渔阳道。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任潜踪匿迹，形影相吊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王承恩拉太子同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "娘娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（静场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "取酒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（费贞娥取酒上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岁在甲申，暮春三月，大明气数，于厮尽矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父王母后啊！值此大难临身，微躯弱质何足为惜。请父王速将佩剑，立斩孩儿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父王也可放心矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！难得，难得！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主 （越恁好） 严亲恩浩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "香消粉散，拚尸骸弃蓬蒿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "瘦怯怯赴泉台茫茫路遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "碎首何堪报。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "崇祯帝 （越恁好） 看剑光闪处节义名标。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崇祯杀死公主。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "娘娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崇祯帝扔剑给娘娘。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "娘娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲儿慢行，做娘的来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（娘娘自刎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁，娘娘自刎了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！死得好，死得好……"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁……"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "费宫人，你逃命去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴婢愿与万岁娘娘共存同亡！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崇祯帝苦笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈，哈……有道是君死为社稷，尔死又何益？你，你逃生去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崇祯帝撕衣襟写血书。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯帝",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朕非亡国主，误国是奸谗。吾尸可碎裂，百姓望垂怜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 家亡国破何足道，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只索向泉台路遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苍天吓，天！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨只恨三百载皇图啊呀一旦抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崇祯帝自管向煤山走去。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "费贞娥 （尾声） 朕非亡国主，误国是奸谗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾尸可碎裂，百姓望垂怜，百姓望垂怜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（费贞娥下。）"
        }
      ],
